'''輔酶B'''（{{lang-en|Coenzyme B}}）是一種[[輔酶|輔酶]]，在[[產甲烷菌|產甲烷菌]]的[[氧化還原反應|氧化還原反應]]中需要被用到。 輔酶B的完整化學名稱為7-巰基庚酰蘇氨酸磷酸酯(7-mercaptoheptanoylthreoninephosphate)<ref>{{cite journal |author=Noll KM, Rinehart KL, Tanner RS, Wolfe RS |title=Structure of component B (7-mercaptoheptanoylthreonine phosphate) of the methylcoenzyme M methylreductase system of Methanobacterium thermoautotrophicum |journal=Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. |volume=83 |issue=12 |pages=4238–42 |year=1986 |pmid=3086878 |doi=10.1073/pnas.83.12.4238 |pmc=323707}}</ref>。分子中含有一個[[巰基|巰基]]，是其最主要進行反應的位置。

輔酶B與2-甲基巰基乙烷磺酸(甲基-[[輔酶M|輔酶M]]，縮寫成{{chem|CH|3|–S–CoM}})反應，在[[產甲烷作用|產甲烷作用]]中釋放出[[甲烷|甲烷]]：<ref>{{cite journal |author=Thauer RK |title=Biochemistry of methanogenesis: a tribute to Marjory Stephenson. 1998 Marjory Stephenson Prize Lecture |journal=Microbiology |volume=144 |issue=Pt 9 |pages=2377–406 |date=September 1998 |pmid=9782487 |url=http://mic.sgmjournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=9782487 |doi=10.1099/00221287-144-9-2377 |access-date=2014-06-26 |archive-date=2020-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517185916/http://http%3a//mic.sgmjournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup%3Fview%3Dlong%26pmid%3D9782487/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
:{{chem|link=輔酶M|CH|3|–S–CoM}} + HS–CoB  →  {{chem|CH|4}}  +  CoB–S–S–CoM
這種轉換的催化[[酵素|酵素]]為[[甲基輔酶M還原酶|甲基輔酶M還原酶]]，它含有[[輔因子F430|輔因子F430]]作為[[輔基|輔基]]。

一種相關轉換，利用到HS-CoB及HS-CoM兩者，由[[延胡索酸還原酶|延胡索酸還原酶]]催化，將[[延胡索酸|延胡索酸]]還原成[[琥珀酸|琥珀酸]]：<ref>{{cite journal |author=Heim S, Künkel A, Thauer RK, Hedderich R |title=Thiol:fumarate reductase (Tfr) from Methanobacterium thermoautotrophicum—identification of the catalytic sites for fumarate reduction and thiol oxidation |journal=Eur. J. Biochem. |volume=253 |issue=1 |pages=292–9 |date=April 1998 |pmid=9578488 |url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/resolve/openurl?genre=article&sid=nlm:pubmed&issn=0014-2956&date=1998&volume=253&issue=1&spage=292 |doi=10.1046/j.1432-1327.1998.2530292.x |access-date=2014-06-26 |archive-date=2020-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200528063158/https://febs.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1046/j.1432-1327.1998.2530292.x?sid=nlm%3Apubmed |dead-url=no }}</ref>
:{{chem|CH|3|–S–CoM}} + HS–CoB  <sup>–</sup>{{chem|O|2|CCH=CHCO|2|-}} →  <sup>–</sup>{{chem|O|2|CCH|2|–CH|2|CO|2|-}}  +  CoB–S–S–CoM

